{"title":"vector","uid":"2d1b6889286b1c5df9dec7e8bb7f8ac5","slug":"vector","date":"2022-09-25T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-09-26T18:49:03.955Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/vector.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fate-zuolun/blog_img@main/202209270248656.jpg","content":"<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>本文主要学习陈小玉老师的《算法训练营》一书</p></blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"vector容器\"><a href=\"#vector容器\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"vector容器\"></a>vector容器</h1><p>vector：是一个封装<strong>动态数组</strong>的顺序容器</p>\n<h2 id=\"头文件\"><a href=\"#头文件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"头文件\"></a>头文件</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">#include&lt;vector&gt;</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"创建\"><a href=\"#创建\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"创建\"></a>创建</h2><p>一个空的vector，数据类型为int，数组名为a</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">vector&lt;int&gt;a;</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<p>如果要指定元素个数：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">vector&lt;int&gt;a(元素个数);</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<p>如果要指定数组中每个元素的初值：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">vector&lt;int&gt;a(元素个数,元素初值);</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>总结：vector&lt;数据类型&gt;数组名(元素个数，元素初值)</strong></p>\n<p>b数组复制a数组，首先<strong>b和a需要同类型</strong>，所以前面声明一个数组b，然后**(被复制的对象)**：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">vector&lt;int&gt;b(a)</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>注意：a和b的地址空间并不相同，也就是更改b并不影响a原来的值</strong></p>\n<p>复制区间[a.begin()+3,a.end()-3),即<em>第四个元素到倒数第四个元素</em>：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">vector&lt;int&gt;b(a.begin()+3,a.end()-3)</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"增加\"><a href=\"#增加\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"增加\"></a>增加</h2><p>尾插指定元素：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">a.push_back(6)</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<p>指定元素头插(位置,元素)<em>让10成为下标为1的元素</em>：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">a.insert(a.begin()+1,10)</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<p>指定元素多次头插(位置,个数,元素)：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">a.insert(a.begin()+1,5,10)</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<p>指定元素头插区间(位置,区间头,区间尾)：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">a.insert(a.begin()+1,b.begin(),b.begin()+3)</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"删除\"><a href=\"#删除\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"删除\"></a>删除</h2><p>尾删：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">a.pop_back()</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<p>删除指定位置的元素：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">a.erase(a.begin())</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<p>删除区间(区间头,区间尾)：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">a.erase(a.begin()+1,a.begin()+3)</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<p>清空向量：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">a.clear()</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"遍历\"><a href=\"#遍历\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"遍历\"></a>遍历</h2><p>下标遍历：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">for(int i &#x3D; 0;i &lt; a.size();i++)\n\tcout &lt;&lt; a[i] &lt;&lt; &quot; &quot;;</code></pre>\n\n<p>迭代器遍历：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">for(vector&lt;int&gt;::iterator it &#x3D; a.begin();it &lt; a.end();it++) &#x2F;&#x2F;定义与容器同种类型的迭代器it\n\tcout &lt;&lt; *it &lt;&lt; endl;</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>迭代器it的使用类似指针,所以取值为：*it</strong> </p>\n<h2 id=\"改变大小\"><a href=\"#改变大小\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"改变大小\"></a>改变大小</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">a.resize(n);</code></pre>\n\n<p>如果：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>resize个数 &gt; 当前向量大小，则填充</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>resize个数 &lt; 当前向量大小，则从最后开始舍弃</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"例题\"><a href=\"#例题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"例题\"></a>例题</h2><p><a href=\"https://vjudge.csgrandeur.cn/problem/HDU-3527\">HDU3527</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"问题重述\"><a href=\"#问题重述\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"问题重述\"></a>问题重述</h3><p>X国有两份名单，一份是之前X-&gt;Y的间谍名单，一份是Y-&gt;X的间谍名单，两份名单存在同一个名字的为双重间谍。现在边境上有一群人将进入X国，但X国只让双重间谍和普通人进来，需要列出需要抓捕的间谍名单。</p>\n<h3 id=\"输入\"><a href=\"#输入\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"输入\"></a>输入</h3><p>有几个测试用例。每个测试用例包含四个部分，第一部分包含3个正整数A、B、C，</p>\n<p>A是进入边境的人数。 B是Y-&gt;X的间谍人数，C是之前X-&gt;Y的间谍人数。  </p>\n<p>第二部分包含A个字符串，进入边境的名单。  </p>\n<p>第二部分包含B个字符串，Y-&gt;X的间谍名单。  </p>\n<p>第二部分包含C字符串，之前X-&gt;Y的间谍名单。  </p>\n<p>在每个测试用例之后都有一个空行。  </p>\n<p>在一个列表中不会出现重复的名字，如果重复的名字出现在两个列表中，他们意味着同一个人。</p>\n<h3 id=\"输出\"><a href=\"#输出\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"输出\"></a>输出</h3><p>按列表B的顺序，依次输出间谍名单，如果没有，则输出“No enemy spy”</p>\n<h3 id=\"分析\"><a href=\"#分析\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"分析\"></a>分析</h3><p>其实只要找到<strong>在Y-&gt;X中，但不在X-&gt;Y</strong>就是Y国的间谍，而我们还需要<strong>判断间谍有没有进入边境</strong></p>\n<h3 id=\"代码\"><a href=\"#代码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"代码\"></a>代码</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">#include&lt;iostream&gt; &#x2F;&#x2F;io \n#include&lt;vector&gt; &#x2F;&#x2F;动态数组的使用 \n#include&lt;string&gt; &#x2F;&#x2F;string类型的使用 \n#include&lt;algorithm&gt; &#x2F;&#x2F;find函数 \nusing namespace std;\n \n&#x2F;&#x2F;定义动态数组 \nvector&lt;string&gt;A;&#x2F;&#x2F;边界的人 \nvector&lt;string&gt;B;&#x2F;&#x2F;Y-&gt;X \nvector&lt;string&gt;C;&#x2F;&#x2F;X-&gt;Y \nvector&lt;string&gt;res;&#x2F;&#x2F;最后结果 \n\nint main()\n&#123;\n\t&#x2F;&#x2F;定义输入的变量 \n\tint a,b,c; \n\tstring s;\n\twhile(cin &gt;&gt; a &gt;&gt; b &gt;&gt; c)\n\t&#123;\n\t\t&#x2F;&#x2F;由于涉及多次输入输出，所以应该先清空动态数组\n\t\tA.clear(),B.clear(),C.clear(),res.clear();\n\t\t\n\t\t&#x2F;&#x2F;将各个容器对应的字符串装好 \n\t\tfor(int i &#x3D; 0;i &lt; a;i++)\n\t\t&#123; \n\t\t\tcin &gt;&gt; s;\n\t\t\tA.push_back(s); \n\t\t&#125; \n\t\t\n\t\tfor(int i &#x3D; 0;i &lt; b;i++)\n\t\t&#123; \n\t\t\tcin &gt;&gt; s;\n\t\t\tB.push_back(s); \n\t\t&#125;\n\t\t\t\n\t\tfor(int i &#x3D; 0;i &lt; c;i++)\n\t\t&#123;\n\t\t\tcin &gt;&gt; s;\n\t\t\tC.push_back(s);\n\t\t&#125;\n\t\t\n\t\tfor(int i &#x3D; 0;i &lt; b;i++)&#x2F;&#x2F;遍历Y-&gt;X\n\t\t&#123;\n\t\t\tif(find(A.begin(),A.end(),B[i])!&#x3D; A.end())&#x2F;&#x2F;迭代器未到最后，即在边界找到了Y-&gt;X的间谍\n\t\t\t&#123;\n\t\t\t\tif(find(C.begin(),C.end(),B[i])&#x3D;&#x3D; C.end())&#x2F;&#x2F;迭代器到最后，即X-&gt;Y的名单没有，即不是双面间谍\t\n\t\t \t\t\tres.push_back(B[i]);&#x2F;&#x2F;将间谍加入结果 \n \t\t\t&#125; \n\t\t&#125;\n\t\t\n\t\tif(res.size() &#x3D;&#x3D; 0)&#x2F;&#x2F;如果结果为空，则无间谍\n\t\t\tcout &lt;&lt; &quot;No enemy spy&quot; &lt;&lt; endl ;\n\t\telse\n\t\t&#123; \n\t\t\tfor(int i &#x3D; 0;i &lt; res.size();i++) \n\t\t\t&#123;\n\t\t\t\tcout &lt;&lt; res[i];\n\t\t\t\tif(i !&#x3D; res.size()-1)&#x2F;&#x2F;防止最后一个字符串有空格 \n\t\t\t\t\tcout &lt;&lt; &quot; &quot;;\n\t\t\t&#125;\n\t\t\tcout &lt;&lt; endl;\n\t\t&#125; \n\t&#125;\n\treturn 0; \n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"程序涉及的函数\"><a href=\"#程序涉及的函数\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"程序涉及的函数\"></a>程序涉及的函数</h2><div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">提示</p>\n<p>find(begin,end,element)：从begin找到end，看是否存在element,如果不存在返回end<br>.size()：容器内的元素个数<br>.clear() ：清空<br>.push_back()：vector插入<br>.begin()：指向容器第一个元素的指针<br>.end() ：指向容器最后一个元素的下个位置的指针</p>\n\n</div>\n<p><strong>如有错误，敬请指正，欢迎交流，谢谢♪(･ω･)ﾉ</strong></p>\n","feature":true,"text":" 本文主要学习陈小玉老师的《算法训练营》一书 vector容器vector：是一个封装动态数组的顺序容器 头文件#include&lt;vector&gt; 创建一个空的vector，数据类型为int，数组名为a vector&lt;int&gt;a; 如果要指定元素个数： ve...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"3.4k","symbolsTime":"3 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"C语言","slug":"C语言","count":3,"path":"api/categories/C语言.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"数据结构","slug":"数据结构","count":3,"path":"api/tags/数据结构.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#vector%E5%AE%B9%E5%99%A8\"><span class=\"toc-text\">vector容器</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%A4%B4%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">头文件</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA\"><span class=\"toc-text\">创建</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">增加</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%88%A0%E9%99%A4\"><span class=\"toc-text\">删除</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%81%8D%E5%8E%86\"><span class=\"toc-text\">遍历</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%94%B9%E5%8F%98%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%8F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">改变大小</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%98\"><span class=\"toc-text\">例题</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E9%87%8D%E8%BF%B0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">问题重述</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5\"><span class=\"toc-text\">输入</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%BE%93%E5%87%BA\"><span class=\"toc-text\">输出</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90\"><span class=\"toc-text\">分析</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81\"><span class=\"toc-text\">代码</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%E6%B6%89%E5%8F%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">程序涉及的函数</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"zuolun","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/img/6.jpg","link":"/","description":"一个啥都不会，正在努力学习的小白","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":{"link":"https://blog.csdn.net/m0_51302822?type=blog"},"juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"queue","uid":"e5a76ab0f6f1083dd6d4bb71a07d1419","slug":"queue","date":"2022-09-26T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-09-27T16:13:18.324Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/queue.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fate-zuolun/blog_img@main/202209270248656.jpg","text":" 本文主要学习陈小玉老师的《算法训练营》一书 queue容器queue是一个先进先出的容器，比如我们排队，先排的往往被先服务，后排的被后服务。 stack和queue的不同 stack：先进后出 queue：先进先出 stack取栈顶：top( ) queue取队头： front...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.7k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"C语言","slug":"C语言","count":3,"path":"api/categories/C语言.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"数据结构","slug":"数据结构","count":3,"path":"api/tags/数据结构.json"}],"author":{"name":"zuolun","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/img/6.jpg","link":"/","description":"一个啥都不会，正在努力学习的小白","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":{"link":"https://blog.csdn.net/m0_51302822?type=blog"},"juejin":"","customs":{}}},"feature":true},"next_post":{"title":"stack","uid":"1932edd6bc286fe1e67c448fee302e6f","slug":"stack","date":"2022-09-25T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-09-26T18:49:00.150Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/stack.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/fate-zuolun/blog_img@main/202209270248656.jpg","text":" 本文主要学习陈小玉老师的《算法训练营》一书 stack容器stack是一个先进后出的容器，比如我们拿一个玻璃瓶装糖果，先下去的糖果往往最后才能拿出来。 stack和vector的不同 vector能对任意位置插入删除，stack只能对栈顶进行操作 vector支持随机访问，st...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.4k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"C语言","slug":"C语言","count":3,"path":"api/categories/C语言.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"数据结构","slug":"数据结构","count":3,"path":"api/tags/数据结构.json"}],"author":{"name":"zuolun","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/img/6.jpg","link":"/","description":"一个啥都不会，正在努力学习的小白","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":{"link":"https://blog.csdn.net/m0_51302822?type=blog"},"juejin":"","customs":{}}},"feature":true}}